#: org.kde.knavalbattle.appdata.xml:9
msgid "Naval Battle"
msgstr "Naval Battle"

#. (itstool) path: component/summary
#: org.kde.knavalbattle.appdata.xml:10
msgid "Battle Ship Game"
msgstr "Kuģu kaujas spēle"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.knavalbattle.appdata.xml:12
msgid ""
"Naval Battle is a ship sinking game. Ships are placed on a board which "
"represents the sea. Players try to hit each others ships in turns without "
"knowing where they are placed. The first player to destroy all ships wins "
"the game."
msgstr ""
"„Naval Battle“ ir kuģu nogremdēšanas spēle. Kuģus spēlētāji novieto laukumā, "
"kas reprezentē jūru. Pēc tam abi spēlētāji mēģina nogremdēt viens otra "
"kuģus, nezinot to atrašanās vietu. Uzvar pirmais, kuram izdodas iznīcināt "
"visus pretinieka kuģus."
